com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.collection

Interface SupportsBatchCreation<ResourceT extends Indexable>

  • Type Parameters:
    ResourceT - the top level Azure resource type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ActiveDirectoryApplications, ApplicationGateways, ApplicationSecurityGroups, AvailabilitySets, DdosProtectionPlans, Disks, ExpressRouteCircuits, Identities, LoadBalancers, NetworkInterfaces, NetworkPeerings, Networks, NetworkSecurityGroups, NetworkWatchers, PublicIPAddresses, ResourceGroups, RoleAssignments, RouteFilters, RouteTables, Snapshots, StorageAccounts, TrafficManagerProfiles, VirtualMachineCustomImages, VirtualMachines, VirtualMachineScaleSets, VirtualNetworkGateways

    public interface SupportsBatchCreation<ResourceT extends Indexable>
    Providing access to creating a batch of Azure top level resources of same type.

    (Note: this interface is not intended to be implemented by user code)
